<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_539_r2l24"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Vicʒtum / Als Jr vns <expan>geſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von einer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_539_r2l25"><expan>cʒweẏdigu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> wegen als Jr vernomen habt / dıe vvir ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_539_r2l27">hinab gen <expan>Mıltemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> geſchickt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc dauon <expan>vviſʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_539_r2l28">vvir niht / vnd bedürfft auch darümb <expan>nẏemand<ex>en</ex></expan> in ver = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_539_r2l30">dehtnüſſe <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough">Vnd </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_539_r2l29"><expan>Dan<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir </ab></add> <expan>bıte<ex>n</ex></expan> ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>fleiſʒıkl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> / Jr vvöllet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_539_r2l31">ew die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hinfür <expan>günſticklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> laſʒen <expan>beuolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_539_r2l32">Als vvir ew des wol <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> / Das wöllen etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_539_r2l33"><expan>Sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Martini Anno xij<hi rend="sup">o</hi> $ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_539" id="269r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
